          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/309__-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the remaining <strong>Dijon</strong> in a small bowl with the <strong>apple cider vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>- this is your<strong> Dijon dressing</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bash the <strong>walnuts</strong> (in the bag with a rolling pin)</p>\r\n<p>Add them to a small heatproof dish and place in the oven for 4 min or until slightly darkened&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
